name: "Green Skull (With Signs)" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Ballpoint pen on notebook page with digital embellishments and color.] The bones never lie. The signs and symbols are clear! The future has been foretold, and if you can interpret the portents correctly, you will prosper! (Unlike the guy whose skull was used to cast this spell... Thanks Phil, by the way! We'll return your braincase to your casket before the New Year!) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
